data.description: This Colonial home has Low Maintenance Vinyl Siding, a Stonewall Entrance, and a Large Paved Circular Driveway that awaits its new owners. This 3 Bedroom home offers a Spacious Primary Bedroom with an Ensuite and a Walk-in Closet.  Stainless-Steel Appliances, Kitchen Island with Breakfast Nook. Sliders in the Dining Room that open to the Back Deck facing the Sizable Backyard. 2.5 Bathrooms. A Laundry Area on the Main Floor. A Stone-faced Fireplace in the Family Room, and A Separate Living Room / Office Space. A 2 Car Garage. This home provides plenty of Space to Entertain. Don't Delay; Schedule your Viewing Today.
